high_descs: Turn left, turn right at the table and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the tomato behind the glass.
Turn right and walk to the sink ahead.
Put the tomato inside of the sink, use water to rinse off the tomato, pick up the tomato from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the right, and look up at the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave door, place the tomato inside the microwave, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off the tomato and put the tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left then walk straight to the counter on beside the left side of the stove
Pick up the tomato on the counter
Turn right then head to the sink on your left
Put the tomato in the sink and rinse it
Turn left then head to the microwave on your right
Open the microwave and put in the tomato
anns.task_desc: Put the clean tomato in the microwave

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to in front of the stove.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean tomato in the microwave.
